        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>6 Queen Anne St | W</placeName>
                    <date>11 Nov 63</date>
                    <salute>Dear M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Conway</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I am sorry to say that I have heard from M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi> Darwin that my Brother is no better &amp; that he is forbidden by his physician to see any one.<ref target="#foot.f1"/> He begs me to say how sorry he is that he cannot have the pleasure of making your acquaintance.</p>
<p>Believe me | Yours very truly | Eras. Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
        </div>

        

        

